JOHANNESBURG - Alastair Bishop from the Big Al Podcast joins The Clinch to debate with Simon which fights they both want to see happen the most this year in the EFC (Extreme Fighting Championship). In the first of this two-part special, they go through the Flyweight, Bantamweight, Featherweight, Lightweight, and Womens' divisions, and deal with Welterweight, Middleweight, Light Heavyweight, and Heavyweight divisions in part 2. eNCA